author: Madeline Roth
title: Finneas Flaunts His Falsetto For ‘One World: Together At Home’ Performance
description: Finneas performs "Let's Fall In Love For The Night" for Global Citizen's "One World: Together At Home" event.
content: It's been a month since Finneas charmed us all with his fancy footwork in the "Let's Fall In Love For The Night" video. Sadly, his latest performance of the song didn't include any of those mesmerizing moves but what it lacked in choreography, it made up for … [+1488 chars]
